WEBVTT

00:01:02.720 --> 00:01:06.960
Jagdish Mahapatra: Mumbai’s Chatrapati
Shivaji terminus, a historic place.

00:01:07.640 --> 00:01:10.936
Very beautiful but busy.

00:01:10.960 --> 00:01:12.616
You all know this.

00:01:12.640 --> 00:01:17.776
Now tell me how many of you
will walk in this jam-packed place

00:01:17.800 --> 00:01:18.857
without any clothes

00:01:18.881 --> 00:01:24.136
wearing a board around your neck
that has all your personal details?

00:01:24.160 --> 00:01:26.920
You would say, “Who does that?
It’s crazy.”

00:01:26.920 --> 00:01:28.540
lt totally is.

00:01:28.760 --> 00:01:35.056
But I can tell you that in the internet
world we are all doing this, all the time.